1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:47,020 --> 00:01:48,570
[Jinhai Kindergarten 61st
Children's Day Play]

4
00:01:49,620 --> 00:01:53,640
You monster, give back my grandpa!

5
00:01:53,729 --> 00:01:55,509
Stay where you are!

6
00:01:55,590 --> 00:01:57,259
[Stop!]

7
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,950
[Run!]

8
00:01:59,030 --> 00:02:00,750
[I'm a monster!]

9
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,390
[I'm the strongest]

10
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,190
[The monster hit us!]

11
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,830
[Mum, I want to go home]

12
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,470
[Angry]

13
00:02:08,370 --> 00:02:09,680
How ridiculous this is!

14
00:02:09,770 --> 00:02:11,410
The Calabash Brothers

15
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:14,320
is ruined by your daughter.

16
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:15,130
As I always say,

17
00:02:15,210 --> 00:02:17,600
you parents should
teach kids positive things.

18
00:02:17,690 --> 00:02:20,230
Why does she worship monsters?

19
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:22,150
Sorry, Miss.

20
00:02:22,329 --> 00:02:23,930
It's not me...

21
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:26,490
Then why did your daughter
shout that her father was a monster

22
00:02:26,579 --> 00:02:28,010
and the full moon would
enhance his strength?

23
00:02:28,090 --> 00:02:30,390
Where did she learn these things?

24
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:32,110
What?

25
00:02:33,810 --> 00:02:34,840
Look at me,

26
00:02:34,940 --> 00:02:36,160
Look at me!

27
00:02:36,970 --> 00:02:38,610
You said that your father is a monster,

28
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:39,640
didn't you?

29
00:02:39,730 --> 00:02:41,450
Not again. Got it?

30
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:42,670
So where's him?

31
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:43,850
Can he come to me?

32
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,470
I want to see him.

33
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:52,100
Okay,

34
00:02:52,490 --> 00:02:53,650
he is a monster.

35
00:02:53,730 --> 00:02:55,200
Satisfied?

36
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:01,020
Go home.

37
00:03:05,330 --> 00:03:07,400
He's a monster!

38
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,500
If not, why haven't I seen him?

39
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:08,940
[Episode 3: Chen Jun He, You Monster]

40
00:03:08,940 --> 00:03:09,760
Monster!

41
00:03:09,850 --> 00:03:10,730
Awful!

42
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:12,590
I hate him!

43
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:18,120
Hurry up!

44
00:03:18,210 --> 00:03:18,920
Why?

45
00:03:19,010 --> 00:03:20,870
To save yourself!

46
00:03:22,610 --> 00:03:23,450
Stop!

47
00:03:23,530 --> 00:03:24,370
Halt!

48
00:03:24,370 --> 00:03:26,010
[Study broadly, study eagerly,
study diligently]

49
00:03:26,730 --> 00:03:27,640
Stop!

50
00:03:29,130 --> 00:03:29,890
Which class are you in?

51
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,210
Don't try to escape.

52
00:03:31,300 --> 00:03:32,390
Follow them!

53
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:33,370
Go with me,

54
00:03:33,450 --> 00:03:34,329
you wretch!

55
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,810
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

56
00:03:37,810 --> 00:03:38,950
Hurry up! Into My house!

57
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:43,310
Slow down!

58
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:52,520
Look at his face, a shoe print.

59
00:03:56,410 --> 00:03:57,390
Why do you laugh?

60
00:03:57,730 --> 00:03:58,900
Sorry.

61
00:04:08,170 --> 00:04:09,370
Why are you looking at me?

62
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:11,150
School's over. Don't you want to go home?

63
00:04:15,250 --> 00:04:16,550
I'm so tired!

64
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:21,050
Do you know him?

65
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,400
Chen Jun He.

66
00:04:22,490 --> 00:04:24,570
A notorious jerk.

67
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:25,770
He always works against teachers!

68
00:04:25,860 --> 00:04:27,110
Why do you mess with him?

69
00:04:32,370 --> 00:04:32,930
Sorry...

70
00:04:33,020 --> 00:04:34,070
we lost them.

71
00:04:34,610 --> 00:04:35,330
Idiot.

72
00:04:35,420 --> 00:04:36,870
They are girls.

73
00:04:38,090 --> 00:04:39,470
But they run fast.

74
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:41,920
Do you guys have a feud?

75
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:43,630
There's a feud

76
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:44,730
between us.

77
00:04:45,100 --> 00:04:46,090
No.

78
00:04:46,170 --> 00:04:47,270
I don't know her.

79
00:04:47,450 --> 00:04:48,840
Never meet her.

80
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,350
What feud?

81
00:04:53,409 --> 00:04:54,400
Don't ask me.

82
00:04:54,490 --> 00:04:55,510
Just a feud.

83
00:04:57,370 --> 00:04:59,080
Why did she give you a kick?

84
00:04:59,250 --> 00:05:00,360
In this community,

85
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,970
she who dares to give you a kick

86
00:05:02,060 --> 00:05:03,490
is not ordinary.

87
00:05:03,580 --> 00:05:04,440
Why don't you tell us

88
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:05,560
what kind of feud it is?

89
00:05:06,650 --> 00:05:08,070
Don't you know him?

90
00:05:08,780 --> 00:05:09,710
I...

91
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,710
Of course not.

92
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,230
Okay.

93
00:05:15,970 --> 00:05:17,320
Don't talk to him.

94
00:05:17,410 --> 00:05:18,630
Stay away from him as far as possible.

95
00:05:18,930 --> 00:05:19,960
If he dares to bother you,

96
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:21,270
his end is near.

97
00:05:21,770 --> 00:05:22,790
What do you mean?

98
00:05:22,980 --> 00:05:24,990
You want to challenge him again?

99
00:05:25,530 --> 00:05:26,470
None of your business.

100
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:27,640
It's mine.

101
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:28,320
Hua.

102
00:05:28,410 --> 00:05:29,290
Don't worry.

103
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:30,400
I'll not step in.

104
00:05:30,490 --> 00:05:31,400
It's beyond my capability.

105
00:05:31,490 --> 00:05:32,550
I will.

106
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:34,040
Take it easy.

107
00:05:34,130 --> 00:05:35,120
Believe in Ba Dan.

108
00:05:35,210 --> 00:05:36,050
He's hailed as

109
00:05:36,130 --> 00:05:37,409
the head of our school.

110
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:38,250
If I need him,

111
00:05:38,330 --> 00:05:39,590
he will definitely help me.

112
00:05:48,950 --> 00:05:49,890
What happened?

113
00:05:50,490 --> 00:05:51,280
Who bullied Qing Tong?

114
00:05:51,370 --> 00:05:52,280
How dare he?

115
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,280
See?

116
00:05:53,370 --> 00:05:54,400
My patron.

117
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:55,530
Don't bother.

118
00:05:55,610 --> 00:05:57,470
What class and which grade is he in?

119
00:05:58,090 --> 00:05:59,120
Class One, Grade Three.

120
00:05:59,210 --> 00:06:00,600
Chen Jun He.

121
00:06:03,850 --> 00:06:04,730
I must leave now.

122
00:06:07,420 --> 00:06:08,300
Li Qing Tong.

123
00:06:08,450 --> 00:06:09,210
We're all schoolmates.

124
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:10,490
Don't be so mean.

125
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:11,880
Remember to say sorry to him.

126
00:06:11,970 --> 00:06:12,850
Are you serious?

127
00:06:14,650 --> 00:06:16,040
Leave immediately!

128
00:06:16,130 --> 00:06:17,950
You jerk.

129
00:06:22,570 --> 00:06:23,250
Boss,

130
00:06:23,330 --> 00:06:25,050
why not wipe the shoe print on your face?

131
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:27,000
Or you'll be scolded.

132
00:06:27,980 --> 00:06:29,230
A shoe print?

133
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,760
So there's a shoe print on my face,

134
00:06:32,850 --> 00:06:34,050
and you guys keep silent.

135
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:36,070
Sorry, we're too busy playing detectives

136
00:06:37,020 --> 00:06:38,000
to notice it.

137
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:39,640
Xiao Huo, help him.

138
00:06:42,130 --> 00:06:43,190
I can wipe it myself.

139
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:47,120
Add some water.

140
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:48,210
Well,

141
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,370
you see,

142
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:52,270
can she come from No. 1 Middle School?

143
00:06:53,930 --> 00:06:54,810
That's one possibility.

144
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:07,790
In my opinion,

145
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,510
you shouldn't go out recently.

146
00:07:11,090 --> 00:07:12,400
And then you won't meet him,

147
00:07:12,490 --> 00:07:13,910
and he won't see you.

148
00:07:14,450 --> 00:07:16,310
Then the page can be turned over.

149
00:07:17,500 --> 00:07:19,920
Why? You acted tough in the afternoon,

150
00:07:22,290 --> 00:07:23,350
and somewhat bold.

151
00:07:25,130 --> 00:07:25,800
Look,

152
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:28,550
you told me to calm down.

153
00:07:28,970 --> 00:07:31,270
So I calmed down.

154
00:07:31,450 --> 00:07:33,050
But once I calmed down,

155
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:36,030
I realised how scary Chen Jun He is.

156
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:38,970
Is he the kind of delinquent
who fights at school?

157
00:07:39,060 --> 00:07:39,650
Maybe.

158
00:07:39,740 --> 00:07:42,270
But I never witnessed it.

159
00:07:42,650 --> 00:07:44,950
All are scared of him,

160
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:46,770
no matter which grade.

161
00:07:46,850 --> 00:07:48,390
We don't know the reason.

162
00:07:52,770 --> 00:07:53,830
Okay.

163
00:07:54,140 --> 00:07:55,570
Luckily, you're not in our school.

164
00:07:55,650 --> 00:07:56,830
You'll not meet him.

165
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:58,790
Maybe he'll forget soon.

166
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:00,200
And there's nothing.

167
00:08:01,540 --> 00:08:02,960
I'm sleepy.

168
00:08:03,130 --> 00:08:04,190
I want to sleep now.

169
00:08:12,890 --> 00:08:13,150
Chen Jun He.

170
00:08:13,150 --> 00:08:14,380
[Men's restroom]

171
00:08:14,380 --> 00:08:15,000
What?

172
00:08:15,090 --> 00:08:17,390
I'm busy now.

173
00:08:21,050 --> 00:08:21,650
You jerk.

174
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:22,910
Get up.

175
00:08:23,770 --> 00:08:26,000
As expected of a jerk who abandons
his wife.

176
00:08:26,090 --> 00:08:27,490
He's been up to no good
since childhood.

177
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:30,390
Why did Li Qing Tong marry him?

178
00:08:32,490 --> 00:08:33,470
Li Qing Tong.

179
00:08:34,570 --> 00:08:36,110
Li Qing Tong.

180
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:38,730
What happened?

181
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:40,039
Listen,

182
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:43,450
in any case,

183
00:08:43,539 --> 00:08:45,240
you mustn't mingle with Chen Jun He.

184
00:08:45,330 --> 00:08:46,350
Am I clear?

185
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:49,120
What?

186
00:08:49,210 --> 00:08:50,370
Be with him?

187
00:08:50,450 --> 00:08:51,680
Got it.

188
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:55,510
Wait,

189
00:08:55,730 --> 00:08:58,190
I should do something
to prevent the tragedy.

190
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,600
Li Qing Tong.

191
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:04,190
Get up.

192
00:09:04,290 --> 00:09:06,160
Why?

193
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:07,650
I want to transfer to your school.

194
00:09:07,730 --> 00:09:08,760
Got it.

195
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:12,720
Sorry?

196
00:09:17,730 --> 00:09:18,160
Qing Tong.

197
00:09:18,250 --> 00:09:20,110
Why are you angry?

198
00:09:20,690 --> 00:09:22,750
Why are you so weird?

199
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:24,290
You messed with Chen Jun He.

200
00:09:24,380 --> 00:09:26,050
And now you want to come to our school.

201
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:27,160
Do you want him to beat you up

202
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,080
or something?

203
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:29,470
I'm not afraid of him.

204
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,010
Though you're not afraid,

205
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:33,110
you cannot ask for trouble.

206
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,810
And how could you go to our school?

207
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:36,830
You didn't study here.

208
00:09:37,210 --> 00:09:38,830
You just don't be with me.

209
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:40,400
I'd better leave here.

210
00:09:40,490 --> 00:09:41,800
I wait for you to come
from school everyday.

211
00:09:41,890 --> 00:09:43,360
A few words and you go to bed.

212
00:09:43,450 --> 00:09:45,030
I'd better leave.

213
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:48,150
Wait.

214
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:51,830
I don't mean that.

215
00:09:52,100 --> 00:09:53,970
I'm worried about that guy.

216
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:55,240
What can I do

217
00:09:55,330 --> 00:09:56,510
if he bullies you?

218
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,880
I desire to go to school with you.

219
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:00,470
It's not for him.

220
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:02,450
And there are so many people,

221
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:03,670
he dares not bully me.

222
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:05,640
You're right.

223
00:10:06,210 --> 00:10:08,750
It's good to study together.

224
00:10:11,260 --> 00:10:11,890
All right.

225
00:10:11,970 --> 00:10:12,570
Fear not.

226
00:10:12,650 --> 00:10:13,530
I'm here for you.

227
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:15,990
Do you agree?

228
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,870
I do.

229
00:10:20,570 --> 00:10:22,590
But the school...

230
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,570
Of course not.

231
00:10:24,660 --> 00:10:25,570
Why not?

232
00:10:25,660 --> 00:10:26,950
Why not,

233
00:10:27,100 --> 00:10:29,520
because there's rules for enrolment.

234
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:31,410
You reckon it's as easy as ABC?

235
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:32,960
Today a cousin comes back from America

236
00:10:33,050 --> 00:10:34,890
and tomorrow another from the country.

237
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:36,250
Do you think anyone
can study here at will?

238
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:37,270
What do you take our school for?

239
00:10:37,570 --> 00:10:38,960
A food market?

240
00:10:39,330 --> 00:10:39,970
Look,

241
00:10:40,060 --> 00:10:40,680
it's out of...

242
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:41,680
Stop it.

243
00:10:41,770 --> 00:10:43,290
It's none of your business.

244
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:43,810
Got it?

245
00:10:43,890 --> 00:10:45,200
Ask her parents to do these.

246
00:10:45,290 --> 00:10:46,840
Just mind your academic performance.

247
00:10:46,930 --> 00:10:48,070
Go and take your class.

248
00:10:49,370 --> 00:10:50,890
Sir,

249
00:10:50,980 --> 00:10:54,190
her parents are not here.

250
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:57,280
Please help us.

251
00:10:57,370 --> 00:10:59,350
You didn't hand in your
composition, did you?

252
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:01,240
Bye, sir.

253
00:11:01,330 --> 00:11:02,400
Come back!

254
00:11:02,860 --> 00:11:04,230
Your composition!

255
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:15,720
What should I do?

256
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,750
Nope.

257
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:23,800
Why don't you tell your parents?

258
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:24,600
Lao Wu said

259
00:11:24,690 --> 00:11:26,720
you had to ask your parents.

260
00:11:27,570 --> 00:11:29,120
If I tell them,

261
00:11:29,210 --> 00:11:31,590
I'll definitely get a "no".

262
00:11:31,970 --> 00:11:34,670
What should we do?

263
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:42,850
Hello?

264
00:11:48,090 --> 00:11:49,950
Why are you here?

265
00:11:50,290 --> 00:11:52,600
Mum, get rid of him!

266
00:11:54,090 --> 00:11:56,120
Still angry with me?

267
00:12:00,770 --> 00:12:01,870
You coward.

268
00:12:01,970 --> 00:12:02,640
What?

269
00:12:02,730 --> 00:12:04,520
Me? Coward?

270
00:12:04,610 --> 00:12:05,690
There are so many people in the world,

271
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:07,630
and you mess with the wrong one.

272
00:12:07,930 --> 00:12:11,080
Nobody dares.

273
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:12,410
I'm not in the mood to talk.

274
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,380
Get out.

275
00:12:14,060 --> 00:12:14,940
Um,

276
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:17,510
I'll come back when you have the mood.

277
00:12:21,450 --> 00:12:22,630
Wait a minute.

278
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:25,390
What?

279
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,790
Do you want a chance to redeem yourself?

280
00:12:33,650 --> 00:12:35,840
No fight.

281
00:12:39,410 --> 00:12:40,750
A piece of cake.

282
00:12:41,130 --> 00:12:42,250
It's easy.

283
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:43,210
Trust me.

284
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:44,200
I'll make it.

285
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:47,810
Do you know how to transfer?

286
00:12:47,890 --> 00:12:49,810
I transferred during junior high.

287
00:12:49,900 --> 00:12:50,400
Hua.

288
00:12:50,490 --> 00:12:51,890
Give me your information.

289
00:12:51,970 --> 00:12:53,210
Then I'll go through the
procedures for you.

290
00:12:53,290 --> 00:12:54,640
and put you in.

291
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:56,170
Sorry,

292
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:58,160
I mean in our school.

293
00:12:58,890 --> 00:12:59,770
What?

294
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:00,960
You want to fake?

295
00:13:01,050 --> 00:13:01,960
No.

296
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,630
You cannot get it.

297
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:05,210
Don't ask me

298
00:13:05,290 --> 00:13:06,450
or I won't help you.

299
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:07,590
Just trust me.

300
00:13:08,130 --> 00:13:09,670
You'd better make it perfect.

301
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,040
Take it easy.

302
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:13,800
Give me two days

303
00:13:14,370 --> 00:13:15,510
and I'll bring you good news.

304
00:13:24,170 --> 00:13:26,100
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

305
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:27,320
[Tieyuan Soda]

306
00:13:34,710 --> 00:13:35,730
[National Secondary School Student
Transfer Form, Li Jin Bu]

307
00:13:35,730 --> 00:13:36,930
You know I have a bro

308
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:39,250
whose family is painting for the cinemas,

309
00:13:39,340 --> 00:13:41,470
equal to an artist.

310
