Look at this paper.

311
00:13:44,130 --> 00:13:45,730
My only comment

312
00:13:45,820 --> 00:13:46,700
is "brilliant".

313
00:13:50,780 --> 00:13:52,870
Is this table handwritten?

314
00:14:00,540 --> 00:14:01,950
And the seal is painted?

315
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:04,300
Let me see.

316
00:14:07,580 --> 00:14:08,080
Well,

317
00:14:08,170 --> 00:14:09,480
it looks like the real one.

318
00:14:09,850 --> 00:14:11,050
I said he was an artist!

319
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:12,440
Well done.

320
00:14:12,570 --> 00:14:13,880
Look at the seal.

321
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:17,500
[Shenzhen No. 6 Middle School]

322
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:21,310
The No. 6 Middle School of Shenzhen City.

323
00:14:22,140 --> 00:14:23,350
What's wrong?

324
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,920
Written by Arabic numerals.

325
00:14:28,010 --> 00:14:29,600
It's so fake.

326
00:14:37,050 --> 00:14:37,800
You're right.

327
00:14:37,890 --> 00:14:38,870
My fault.

328
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:39,300
[Shenzhen No. 6 Middle School]

329
00:14:39,300 --> 00:14:40,320
Is he serious?

330
00:14:40,410 --> 00:14:41,800
So irresponsible.

331
00:14:42,850 --> 00:14:44,490
I declare that from now

332
00:14:44,580 --> 00:14:45,770
he's not my bro.

333
00:14:45,850 --> 00:14:47,470
How unreliable he is!

334
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:49,770
You...

335
00:14:49,860 --> 00:14:51,430
You are kidding us.

336
00:14:52,010 --> 00:14:53,160
The meal is on you.

337
00:14:57,290 --> 00:14:58,510
What should I do?

338
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:00,010
In this dream,

339
00:15:00,100 --> 00:15:02,510
I cannot have a legal identity.

340
00:15:02,850 --> 00:15:04,710
What to do next?

341
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:37,170
Excuse me,

342
00:15:37,260 --> 00:15:39,170
have you ever seen a man
selling sugar-coated haws.

343
00:15:39,260 --> 00:15:40,270
No.

344
00:15:40,780 --> 00:15:41,910
Thank you.

345
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:50,880
Excuse me,

346
00:15:50,970 --> 00:15:53,160
have you ever seen a man
selling sugar-coated haws.

347
00:15:53,250 --> 00:15:54,840
Sorry, I haven't.

348
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,090
Someone with a beard?

349
00:15:56,170 --> 00:15:57,270
Nope.

350
00:15:57,650 --> 00:15:58,170
Thank you.

351
00:15:58,250 --> 00:15:59,360
You can seek

352
00:15:59,450 --> 00:16:00,120
elsewhere.

353
00:16:00,210 --> 00:16:01,090
Let's go.

354
00:16:20,400 --> 00:16:22,160
[Screening House]

355
00:16:47,150 --> 00:16:49,670
[Smart IC Phone]

356
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:25,349
Lin Jin Bu.

357
00:17:25,810 --> 00:17:27,109
What are you doing here?

358
00:17:30,330 --> 00:17:31,230
What?

359
00:17:31,890 --> 00:17:32,950
What's wrong?

360
00:17:33,930 --> 00:17:34,950
It doesn't matter.

361
00:17:35,490 --> 00:17:36,910
Don't worry about me.

362
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,150
When are you leaving?

363
00:17:45,370 --> 00:17:47,560
I'll leave soon.

364
00:17:47,690 --> 00:17:48,760
Just leave.

365
00:17:57,530 --> 00:18:05,390
[Screening House]

366
00:18:20,850 --> 00:18:22,910
What are you going to do?

367
00:18:24,450 --> 00:18:26,280
So weird.

368
00:18:28,580 --> 00:18:32,900
[Screening House]

369
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:46,470
What are you doing?

370
00:18:47,050 --> 00:18:47,990
To accompany you.

371
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:57,080
Why?

372
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,840
Just go home.

373
00:18:59,010 --> 00:18:59,960
No.

374
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:01,670
I'll come back after you.

375
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:44,350
I'm fine.

376
00:19:44,450 --> 00:19:45,330
Take it.

377
00:19:47,010 --> 00:19:47,730
Share it together.

378
00:19:47,820 --> 00:19:48,700
Perfect.

379
00:19:59,940 --> 00:20:01,680
So what are you waiting for?

380
00:20:04,930 --> 00:20:06,550
A call.

381
00:20:07,810 --> 00:20:09,440
You've been waiting for hours.

382
00:20:09,530 --> 00:20:11,070
Are you sure someone will call you?

383
00:20:15,490 --> 00:20:16,670
I don't know.

384
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:18,630
Take a chance.

385
00:20:18,970 --> 00:20:20,750
It's not your field.

386
00:20:23,580 --> 00:20:24,460
All right.

387
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,560
And I want to take a chance here, too.

388
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:29,550
For what?

389
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:31,400
It's not your field.

390
00:20:31,530 --> 00:20:33,480
Don't imitate me.

391
00:20:56,500 --> 00:21:02,330
[Screening House]

392
00:21:02,420 --> 00:21:06,740
[Love Letter]

393
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:09,690
[Peony Hotel]

394
00:21:15,970 --> 00:21:17,370
I don't want to be mean,

395
00:21:17,450 --> 00:21:18,760
but what are you doing?

396
00:21:18,850 --> 00:21:20,610
Went out with a quilt?

397
00:21:20,700 --> 00:21:22,390
Are you crazy?

398
00:21:23,780 --> 00:21:24,680
Look.

399
00:21:24,770 --> 00:21:25,560
Look at your quilt.

400
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:27,170
So dirty.

401
00:21:27,250 --> 00:21:28,530
Satisfied?

402
00:21:28,620 --> 00:21:30,310
Have a fever.

403
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:31,880
Don't stare at me.

404
00:21:31,970 --> 00:21:34,510
Do you want to rush with a quilt?

405
00:21:34,780 --> 00:21:36,470
Do you?

406
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:40,190
Are you crazy?

407
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:43,190
Take it.

408
00:21:44,810 --> 00:21:45,790
Bitter?

409
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:49,080
Take all of this.

410
00:21:49,420 --> 00:21:50,990
Drink slowly.

411
00:21:52,610 --> 00:21:53,710
Who is that?

412
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:57,030
Hello, your letter.

413
00:21:57,130 --> 00:21:58,270
For whom?

414
00:21:59,690 --> 00:22:00,840
Thank you.

415
00:22:03,010 --> 00:22:03,950
Hua.

416
00:22:05,820 --> 00:22:06,700
Hua.

417
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,760
Hua.

418
00:22:09,170 --> 00:22:09,920
Your letter.

419
00:22:10,010 --> 00:22:10,720
Mine?

420
00:22:10,810 --> 00:22:12,280
Here's your name.

421
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:13,680
Sent by your mum?

422
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:14,670
Thank you, Aunt.

423
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:21,970
[High School Admission Letter,
Li Jin Bu]

424
00:22:29,910 --> 00:22:32,430
[Student form]

425
00:22:35,240 --> 00:22:37,720
[Tieyuan Agricultural Bank]

426
00:22:42,130 --> 00:22:42,250
"Go to the school directly.
Here's your tuition fee. No thanks."

427
00:22:42,250 --> 00:22:46,200
[Just enrol. There's money
in the book. Don't worry.]

428
00:22:54,310 --> 00:22:56,010
[High School Admission Letter,
Li Jin Bu]

429
00:22:56,010 --> 00:22:57,910
Where did you get this?

430
00:22:58,410 --> 00:23:00,710
Who conjured it up, your fairy godmother?

431
00:23:00,890 --> 00:23:01,810
My mother.

432
00:23:01,900 --> 00:23:03,250
I called her.

433
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:05,000
And she made it.

434
00:23:06,010 --> 00:23:08,440
You said she would not agree.

435
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:10,000
Obviously, it's different now.

436
00:23:10,090 --> 00:23:11,090
She's changed her mind.

437
00:23:11,180 --> 00:23:12,480
It's up to me.

438
00:23:13,650 --> 00:23:14,910
Wow, well done.

439
00:23:16,340 --> 00:23:18,240
In case of any accident,

440
00:23:18,330 --> 00:23:19,650
may you ask your teacher tomorrow

441
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:20,990
to ensure whether it works or not?

442
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:22,210
Okay.

443
00:23:25,260 --> 00:23:26,270
What are you doing?

444
00:23:26,410 --> 00:23:27,080
Look,

445
00:23:27,170 --> 00:23:28,570
I have much new stationery.

446
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:30,040
My dad bought me

447
00:23:30,130 --> 00:23:30,730
a new backpack

448
00:23:30,810 --> 00:23:31,800
in Shenyang.

449
00:23:31,890 --> 00:23:32,530
Awesome?

450
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:33,200
It's yours now.

451
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:34,410
And a new pencil case.

452
00:23:34,500 --> 00:23:35,880
Yours, too.

453
00:23:35,970 --> 00:23:37,050
And many new pens...

454
00:23:37,140 --> 00:23:39,880
Fan Shui Shui has bought me some new pens.

455
00:23:41,250 --> 00:23:42,840
Where are they?

456
00:23:58,770 --> 00:24:02,600
[No. 3 Middle School]

457
00:24:05,970 --> 00:24:06,870
What are you doing?

458
00:24:14,270 --> 00:24:14,750
Boss,

459
00:24:14,830 --> 00:24:15,680
the girl who kicked you

460
00:24:15,770 --> 00:24:17,050
couldn't be our schoolmate.

461
00:24:17,130 --> 00:24:18,370
I've been observing for days.

462
00:24:18,450 --> 00:24:19,800
She never appeared in our school.

463
00:24:19,950 --> 00:24:20,320
Right.

464
00:24:20,410 --> 00:24:21,730
I've searched every class.

465
00:24:21,820 --> 00:24:23,250
No result.

466
00:24:23,340 --> 00:24:25,210
Then look for her gang,

467
00:24:25,290 --> 00:24:26,990
the two in our school uniforms.

468
00:24:28,010 --> 00:24:29,110
Let's go, Da Da.

469
00:24:31,870 --> 00:24:33,850
[Jeff Chang, "Forgiveness"]

470
00:24:43,410 --> 00:24:44,430
Hua.

471
00:24:47,890 --> 00:24:48,720
Good news!

472
00:24:48,810 --> 00:24:49,920
It's done.

473
00:24:50,010 --> 00:24:51,410
You can go to our school tomorrow.

474
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:52,370
So soon?

475
00:24:52,450 --> 00:24:55,130
You can go to school with me tomorrow.

476
00:24:55,210 --> 00:24:57,010
And supervise your study.

477
00:24:57,090 --> 00:24:57,970
What?

478
00:25:02,940 --> 00:25:06,310
Congratulations!

479
00:25:11,170 --> 00:25:11,600
To be honest,

480
00:25:11,690 --> 00:25:12,560
I'm not blowing...

481
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:13,880
For the first time I met Hua,

482
00:25:13,970 --> 00:25:14,560
I knew

483
00:25:14,650 --> 00:25:16,360
she would be in our class.

484
00:25:17,090 --> 00:25:17,840
Come on.

485
00:25:17,930 --> 00:25:19,510
You said that when we met.

486
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:21,250
Keep at a distance, please.

487
00:25:21,340 --> 00:25:22,680
I'd better we're strangers.

488
00:25:22,770 --> 00:25:24,040
So do I.

489
00:25:24,130 --> 00:25:25,120
Look at your chubby face

490
00:25:25,210 --> 00:25:26,720
covered by bangs.

491
00:25:26,970 --> 00:25:27,640
How dare you?

492
00:25:27,730 --> 00:25:28,640
want to see it clearly?

493
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,400
Come on, guy.

494
00:25:29,490 --> 00:25:30,250
Sorry.

495
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:31,270
My fault.

496
00:25:32,850 --> 00:25:33,730
I tell you,

497
00:25:34,420 --> 00:25:35,870
I'm a gentleman.

498
00:25:39,730 --> 00:25:40,400
Hua.

499
00:25:40,490 --> 00:25:41,520
Seriously,

500
00:25:41,610 --> 00:25:43,160
if someone tries to pick on you,

501
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:44,210
you can say that you're my friend.

502
00:25:44,290 --> 00:25:45,450
I, Wang Xiao Min,

503
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:47,520
am a big name in our school.

504
00:25:50,070 --> 00:25:51,250
A big name

505
00:25:51,330 --> 00:25:52,930
scared by the name of Chen Jun He.

506
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:53,670
Isn't you?

507
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:55,030
Shame on you.

508
00:25:56,540 --> 00:25:58,310
I was worried

509
00:25:58,500 --> 00:26:00,530
that the conflict
between us, the big shots,

510
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:01,950
would implicate you.

511
00:26:02,500 --> 00:26:04,010
Big shots?

512
00:26:04,090 --> 00:26:04,960
Seriously?

513
00:26:05,050 --> 00:26:07,920
Chased by kids of junior high
school and lost your shoes.

514
00:26:08,010 --> 00:26:10,230
Good job.

515
00:26:10,590 --> 00:26:11,470
Um,

516
00:26:11,650 --> 00:26:12,980
it's not my fault.

517
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:14,400
The shoes

518
00:26:14,490 --> 00:26:15,470
are not suitable.

519
00:26:15,650 --> 00:26:16,740
It's too big for me.

520
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:17,880
Stop your nonsense.

521
00:26:19,130 --> 00:26:20,240
Hurry up.

522
00:26:20,330 --> 00:26:22,180
I'd like to buy Hua
book covers after dinner.

523
00:26:22,530 --> 00:26:24,550
I'll help Hua cover her textbooks.

524
00:26:25,530 --> 00:26:26,200
Here.

525
00:26:26,290 --> 00:26:27,050
Have this, Fan Shui Shui.

526
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:27,960
You're welcome.

527
00:26:28,050 --> 00:26:28,600
Meat's raw.

528
00:26:28,690 --> 00:26:29,710
You can have the charcoal.

529
00:26:30,050 --> 00:26:31,350
You have the pot.

530
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:32,120
Lady first.

531
00:26:32,210 --> 00:26:33,400
You have a bottle.

532
00:26:37,770 --> 00:26:40,710
Why are you twisting
your body like a caterpillar?

533
00:26:41,810 --> 00:26:43,010
I'm too excited.

534
00:26:43,100 --> 00:26:45,410
We can go to school together tomorrow.

535
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:46,750
Last time

536
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:48,370
was a decade and more years ago.

537
00:26:48,460 --> 00:26:51,480
Yesterday once more.

538
00:26:51,570 --> 00:26:53,790
Were we good friends during childhood?

539
00:26:54,180 --> 00:26:55,360
You forget?

540
00:26:55,450 --> 00:26:57,610
We were best friends at that time.

541
00:26:57,700 --> 00:26:58,800
Although

542
00:26:58,940 --> 00:27:00,870
you were kind of spoiled,

543
00:27:01,170 --> 00:27:01,990
tearful,

544
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:02,920
mean,

545
00:27:03,010 --> 00:27:04,590
and never shared food with me.

546
00:27:06,130 --> 00:27:07,320
But now look at you,

547
00:27:07,410 --> 00:27:09,110
you've changed a lot.

548
00:27:09,650 --> 00:27:10,730
More beautiful

549
00:27:10,820 --> 00:27:12,120
and clever.

550
00:27:13,170 --> 00:27:15,510
It seems that the south is liveable.

551
00:27:16,370 --> 00:27:17,670
Miraculous.

552
00:27:17,980 --> 00:27:19,730
If I used to be bad to you,

553
00:27:19,820 --> 00:27:21,250
why are you so kind to me now?

554
00:27:21,330 --> 00:27:23,240
No idea.

555
00:27:23,530 --> 00:27:24,450
This time when I met you,

556
00:27:24,530 --> 00:27:26,030
I felt as if

557
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:28,080
we were families.

558
00:27:29,010 --> 00:27:30,850
Of course we are not.

559
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:32,250
You're beautiful now,

560
00:27:32,330 --> 00:27:33,480
but less than me.

561
00:27:36,250 --> 00:27:37,530
I mean that

562
00:27:37,610 --> 00:27:39,210
I hope you can be my family.

563
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:40,990
Thus we can live together.

564
00:27:41,850 --> 00:27:42,810
We should go to school tomorrow.

565
00:27:42,890 --> 00:27:43,770
Sleep now.

566
00:27:54,500 --> 00:27:57,590
Well, life is unpredictable.

567
00:27:57,970 --> 00:27:59,810
I never dream that

568
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:02,600
I can be Li Qing Tong's classmate

569
00:28:02,690 --> 00:28:04,240
and study in the same classroom.

570
00:28:04,330 --> 00:28:06,000
And I'm even given the chance to face

571
00:28:06,090 --> 00:28:08,870
the man I should call he father.

572
00:28:10,780 --> 00:28:11,880
Maybe this is the meaning

573
00:28:12,250 --> 00:28:15,280
of my time-travelling.

574
00:28:29,290 --> 00:28:31,070
Mum, we're going to school!

575
00:28:36,600 --> 00:28:37,620
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

576
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:40,360
Morning, Miss.

577
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,140
Morning, Miss.

578
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:46,790
Good morning, Miss.

579
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:47,560
Morning, Miss Yang.

580
00:28:47,650 --> 00:28:48,140
You two, halt.

581
00:28:48,230 --> 00:28:49,110
Good morning, Miss.

582
00:28:49,600 --> 00:28:50,630
Morning, Miss.

583
00:28:51,600 --> 00:28:53,430
Morning, Miss!

584
00:28:54,490 --> 00:28:55,630
Who's she?

585
00:28:55,970 --> 00:28:57,360
Director of students, Miss Yang.

586
00:28:57,450 --> 00:28:59,160
A nuisance.

587
00:28:59,250 --> 00:29:01,360
She always stands
here with an unkind face,

588
00:29:01,450 --> 00:29:03,000
or looks for students who
violate school rules in corridors.

589
00:29:03,090 --> 00:29:03,930
You know what,

590
00:29:04,020 --> 00:29:07,120
she's the most unpopular
teacher in our school.

591
00:29:07,250 --> 00:29:08,360
You look good in red.

592
00:29:08,450 --> 00:29:09,810
Where did you buy these clothes?

593
00:29:10,130 --> 00:29:12,910
I bought it last week in Xinanlian Plaza.

594
00:29:13,130 --> 00:29:14,830
And the pink backpack?

595
00:29:14,940 --> 00:29:16,430
Also a new one.

596
00:29:16,710 --> 00:29:20,030
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

597
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:29,680
That

598
00:29:29,850 --> 00:29:31,340
is Lin Xue Wei.

599
00:29:31,540 --> 00:29:34,550
You know, the girl who fancies
herself as the belle of the school.

600
00:29:37,650 --> 00:29:38,880
She's our monitor.

601
00:29:38,970 --> 00:29:40,070
It doesn't matter.

602
00:29:40,370 --> 00:29:42,320
She's really exaggerated.

603
00:29:42,570 --> 00:29:44,850
She said her clothes were imported.

604
00:29:44,930 --> 00:29:46,400
Ridiculous.

605
00:29:46,570 --> 00:29:48,730
Labels of imported clothing
are written by foreign languages,

606
00:29:48,820 --> 00:29:49,730
but hers are not.

607
00:29:49,820 --> 00:29:50,840
I've checked it!

608
00:29:50,930 --> 00:29:51,770
You have?

609
00:29:51,850 --> 00:29:53,670
Really?

610
00:29:53,980 --> 00:29:55,770
To collect information for you.

611
00:29:55,860 --> 00:29:56,970
You should be clear

612
00:29:57,060 --> 00:29:58,880
about who you can be friends with.

613
00:29:58,970 --> 00:30:01,070
Just pay attention to yourself.

614
00:30:04,220 --> 00:30:04,810
Hurry up.

615
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:05,920
Chen Jun He is coming.

616
00:30:06,010 --> 00:30:06,530
Hurry up.

617
00:30:06,610 --> 00:30:07,670
Run.

618
00:30:11,310 --> 00:30:17,020
[Study broadly, study eagerly,
study diligently]

619
00:30:20,570 --> 00:30:22,070
Who's on duty today?

620
00:30:22,970 --> 00:30:24,360
Clean the blackboard.

621
00:30:36,370 --> 00:30:37,250
Stand here.

622
00:30:37,340 --> 00:30:39,990
Mr Wu will point you to your seat.

623
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:43,210
Mr Wu.

624
00:30:43,330 --> 00:30:44,510
She's Li Jin Bu.

625
00:30:44,820 --> 00:30:45,700
Back to your seat.

626
00:30:47,460 --> 00:30:48,340
Li Jin Bu?

627
00:30:48,810 --> 00:30:49,880
Have we met before?

628
00:30:50,610 --> 00:30:51,530
Guys,

629
00:30:51,610 --> 00:30:53,850
today we have two new classmates.

630
00:30:53,940 --> 00:30:54,950
The first one is Li Jin Bu,

631
00:30:55,500 --> 00:30:57,290
transferring from Shenzhen.

632
00:30:57,380 --> 00:30:58,630
A self-introduction, please.

633
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,610
Hi guys, I'm Li Jin Bu.

634
00:31:00,730 --> 00:31:02,710
Nice to meet you.

635
00:31:03,130 --> 00:31:04,190
Let's clap for her.

636
00:31:08,140 --> 00:31:09,020
And the other...

637
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,340
Hello?

638
00:31:10,810 --> 00:31:11,690
I'm here!

639
00:31:12,610 --> 00:31:13,210
Morning sir!

640
00:31:13,290 --> 00:31:14,170
Morning guys!

641
00:31:14,330 --> 00:31:15,230
Get off.

642
00:31:17,130 --> 00:31:18,170
My name is Wang Xiao Min.

643
00:31:18,260 --> 00:31:18,810
I used to be in Class Two.

644
00:31:18,890 --> 00:31:19,760
We are old friends.

645
00:31:19,850 --> 00:31:20,810
So no need for an introduction.

646
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:22,120
I just take my seat.

647
00:31:24,050 --> 00:31:26,110
Okay, I didn't expect more.

648
00:31:26,570 --> 00:31:28,160
Li Jin Bu, that's your seat.

649
00:31:35,890 --> 00:31:36,870
Keep quiet.

650
00:31:37,450 --> 00:31:38,120
Class begins.

651
00:31:38,210 --> 00:31:39,160
Stand up.

652
00:31:40,330 --> 00:31:41,120
Morning boys and girls.

653
00:31:41,210 --> 00:31:44,080
Good morning, sir.

654
00:31:44,170 --> 00:31:45,050
Sit down, please.

655
00:31:45,970 --> 00:31:47,270
Turn on your books.

656
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:55,530
Excuse me?

657
00:31:56,930 --> 00:31:57,830
Come in.

658
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,520
Mr Wu.

659
00:32:02,280 --> 00:32:04,890
You know, my heart is with you.

660
00:32:05,460 --> 00:32:07,370
I've long wanted to come to Class Three.

661
00:32:07,460 --> 00:32:09,400
And this dream

662
00:32:09,490 --> 00:32:11,270
is all because of you.

663
00:32:11,370 --> 00:32:12,280
In my mind,

664
00:32:12,450 --> 00:32:13,750
you're the best teacher

665
00:32:14,130 --> 00:32:15,950
in our grade.

666
00:32:16,090 --> 00:32:17,680
Can you leave my class with your heart?

667
00:32:19,050 --> 00:32:20,160
My low blood pressure

668
00:32:20,250 --> 00:32:21,790
is an eyesore for you?

669
00:32:23,420 --> 00:32:24,300
Sir,

670
00:32:24,450 --> 00:32:25,530
don't tell jokes.

671
00:32:25,620 --> 00:32:27,050
Do you know Mr Ma is in hospital

672
00:32:27,140 --> 00:32:28,190
for his high blood pressure?

673
00:32:28,850 --> 00:32:29,730
Yep.

674
00:32:29,930 --> 00:32:31,320
My mother is also here.

675
00:32:31,410 --> 00:32:32,390
To look after him.

676
00:32:33,370 --> 00:32:35,870
You have the cheek to say that?

677
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:38,040
All teachers in Grade Three

678
00:32:38,380 --> 00:32:39,750
have high blood pressure.

679
00:32:39,850 --> 00:32:41,370
It's all your credit.

680
00:32:41,460 --> 00:32:42,280
I'm the exception.

681
00:32:42,370 --> 00:32:42,720
You know what,

682
00:32:42,810 --> 00:32:44,090
if I didn't accept you,

683
00:32:44,170 --> 00:32:45,550
you were home now.

684
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,410
Can I go home?

685
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:49,170
Um,

686
00:32:49,260 --> 00:32:50,760
can you tell my parents

687
00:32:50,850 --> 00:32:52,050
that I can leave school?

688
00:32:52,140 --> 00:32:53,120
You ask for it.

689
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,490
Just a joke.

690
00:32:55,780 --> 00:32:56,970
Wang Xiao Min,

691
00:32:57,050 --> 00:32:57,650
I warn you in advance,

692
00:32:57,740 --> 00:32:59,170
that if you don't study hard

693
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:00,670
and make trouble in my class,

694
00:33:01,170 --> 00:33:03,310
I'll show no mercy

695
00:33:03,410 --> 00:33:04,160
and go to your home

696
00:33:04,250 --> 00:33:05,210
everyday.

697
00:33:05,290 --> 00:33:06,470
I always keep my word.

698
00:33:08,370 --> 00:33:09,560
Got it, sir.

699
00:33:09,650 --> 00:33:11,410
I'll study hard and obey rules.

700
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:12,430
That's good boy.

701
00:33:22,330 --> 00:33:23,210
Mr Wu.

702
00:33:23,380 --> 00:33:24,640
Spring Festival is coming.

703
00:33:24,730 --> 00:33:26,720
My dad wants to buy you a beeper.

704
00:33:26,810 --> 00:33:27,950
I can't be bought.

705
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:30,320
Or a palm phone?

706
00:33:30,450 --> 00:33:31,960
Do you want to be expelled?

707
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:33,320
Sorry sir.

708
00:33:33,410 --> 00:33:34,320
I'll work hard

709
00:33:34,410 --> 00:33:35,710
and bring you honour.

710
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:37,150
Bye, sir.

711
00:33:38,470 --> 00:33:39,540
Ha, the lad.

712
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:40,890
Mr Wu.

713
00:33:41,610 --> 00:33:42,410
You can have more green tea.

714
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:43,440
Good for your blood pressure.

715
00:33:43,530 --> 00:33:43,920
Come back!

716
00:33:44,010 --> 00:33:44,910
You wretch.

717
00:33:48,810 --> 00:33:50,490
He's so hard to control.

718
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:56,000
Ask Mr Wu to change your seat.

719
00:33:56,090 --> 00:33:57,010
It's not good.

720
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:58,940
Why?

721
00:34:00,370 --> 00:34:01,600
The guy

722
00:34:01,690 --> 00:34:03,040
is a nerd.

723
00:34:03,130 --> 00:34:04,790
How dare you.

724
00:34:05,490 --> 00:34:06,680
He's the top student in our grade.

725
00:34:06,770 --> 00:34:08,830
Very smart.

726
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:10,139
You know,

727
00:34:10,370 --> 00:34:11,050
he's tall

728
00:34:11,139 --> 00:34:11,889
and handsome.

729
00:34:11,969 --> 00:34:13,510
He's absolute perfection.

730
00:34:13,929 --> 00:34:15,590
Who are you talking about?

731
00:34:16,050 --> 00:34:17,670
Your deskmate.

732
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:18,760
What's more,

733
00:34:18,850 --> 00:34:20,850
he's the Prince Charming

734
00:34:20,940 --> 00:34:22,280
Li Qing Tong's been
secretly obsessing over

735
00:34:22,370 --> 00:34:23,780
since Grade One.

736
00:34:24,170 --> 00:34:25,090
It's not obsession.

737
00:34:25,170 --> 00:34:25,770
It's admiration.

738
00:34:25,860 --> 00:34:26,989
Got it?

739
00:34:27,330 --> 00:34:28,090
Sure,

740
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:28,770
you've admired him

741
00:34:28,860 --> 00:34:30,489
for one year,

742
00:34:30,570 --> 00:34:31,250
since Grade One.

743
00:34:31,330 --> 00:34:32,960
Never get his attention

744
00:34:33,050 --> 00:34:34,719
nor active contact.

745
00:34:34,810 --> 00:34:35,790
Really interesting.

746
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:36,980
Stop it.

747
00:34:37,730 --> 00:34:39,080
Okay.

748
00:34:39,570 --> 00:34:40,750
What are you eating? I'm joining you.

749
00:34:42,449 --> 00:34:43,830
It's not for you.

750
00:34:44,090 --> 00:34:45,870
Why don't you care about your poor pal?

751
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:46,810
I'm in low blood sugar level.

752
00:34:46,900 --> 00:34:48,070
Give me one.

753
00:34:48,290 --> 00:34:49,830
Before eating, explain your reason

754
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:51,550
for transferring to our class.

755
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:52,790
What's your motive?

756
00:34:53,699 --> 00:34:55,310
Isn't it obvious?

757
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,950
To be with you.

758
00:34:58,690 --> 00:35:00,320
As if I'm going to believe that.

759
00:35:00,660 --> 00:35:03,160
Don't doubt my heart.

760
00:35:04,260 --> 00:35:05,320
Your heart is

761
00:35:05,410 --> 00:35:06,300
with Elva Hsiao.

762
00:35:06,390 --> 00:35:07,750
Not me.

763
00:35:08,370 --> 00:35:09,910
You don't know about this.

764
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:11,010
In my heart,

765
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:13,470
you are in the same position with her.

766
00:35:13,650 --> 00:35:15,840
Um, just back a little more.

767
00:35:17,260 --> 00:35:17,660
Can I beg you for

768
00:35:17,750 --> 00:35:20,000
much more?

769
00:35:20,810 --> 00:35:21,910
Oh, come on.

770
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:23,350
Give me one.

771
00:35:24,180 --> 00:35:24,800
Just one.

772
00:35:24,890 --> 00:35:25,240
No way.

773
00:35:25,330 --> 00:35:25,730
You're so mean.

774
00:35:25,810 --> 00:35:27,070
One, please?

775
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:40,750
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

776
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,220
[Mathematics]

777
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:20,890
Hello,

778
00:36:20,980 --> 00:36:22,040
I'm new here.

779
00:36:22,130 --> 00:36:23,230
I'm Li Jin Bu.

780
00:36:25,140 --> 00:36:26,040
Wu Zhi Xun.

781
00:36:42,170 --> 00:36:43,150
You're back.

782
00:36:47,290 --> 00:36:48,860
Good news, guys.

783
00:36:48,950 --> 00:36:49,960
Your classmate Wu Zhi Xun,

784
00:36:50,050 --> 00:36:51,050
on behalf of our school,

785
00:36:51,140 --> 00:36:52,950
participated in the
Mathematical Olympiad of our city.

786
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:55,560
He's the only liberal arts student

787
00:36:55,650 --> 00:36:56,850
who entered the finals
and got a gold award.

788
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,230
Clap for him!

789
00:37:02,730 --> 00:37:04,530
Mr Wu is interesting.

790
00:37:04,610 --> 00:37:06,330
Clap for everything.

791
00:37:06,420 --> 00:37:08,230
Was he a stand-up comedian?

792
00:37:08,530 --> 00:37:10,230
You're so talkative, Wang Xiao Min.

793
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:10,960
I'm talking here

794
00:37:11,050 --> 00:37:11,610
and you're talking there.

795
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:12,170
Come up here and talk.

796
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:13,140
Come here.

797
00:37:13,250 --> 00:37:13,810
No,

798
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:14,840
you heard it wrong, sir.

799
00:37:14,930 --> 00:37:15,870
I didn't say anything.

800
00:37:15,950 --> 00:37:16,770
I was clapping,

801
00:37:16,860 --> 00:37:17,870
fix-minded.

802
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:18,830
It's the sound of applause.

803
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:19,440
Well done.

804
00:37:19,530 --> 00:37:20,410
Full of energy.

805
00:37:20,570 --> 00:37:21,150
Monitor.

806
00:37:21,230 --> 00:37:21,540
Here.

807
00:37:21,630 --> 00:37:22,520
He's on duty this week.

808
00:37:22,610 --> 00:37:23,870
Wipe the blackboard.

809
00:37:25,220 --> 00:37:26,100
Two weeks.

810
00:37:27,610 --> 00:37:28,490
Class begins.

811
00:37:41,010 --> 00:37:42,790
Keep quiet, the last row.

812
00:37:52,650 --> 00:37:53,490
Chen Jun He.

813
00:37:53,570 --> 00:37:54,450
Come here.

814
00:38:00,540 --> 00:38:02,320
Come here with your chair.

815
00:38:12,780 --> 00:38:13,280
Come on.

816
00:38:13,370 --> 00:38:14,040
Sit here.

817
00:38:14,130 --> 00:38:15,010
Come here.

818
00:38:20,050 --> 00:38:21,750
Had a good chat, lad?

819
00:38:22,410 --> 00:38:23,840
Don't bother your classmates.

820
00:38:23,930 --> 00:38:25,400
Talk to me.

821
00:38:26,210 --> 00:38:26,680
Sir,

822
00:38:26,770 --> 00:38:28,920
we don't have common topics.

823
00:38:29,580 --> 00:38:31,040
You can have a think now.

824
00:38:31,430 --> 00:38:33,030
And then we can have a talk.

825
00:38:33,340 --> 00:38:34,590
Guys, look at the blackboard.

826
00:38:37,770 --> 00:38:39,000
Look at the blackboard.

827
00:38:39,090 --> 00:38:40,750
Listen to the teacher.

828
00:38:48,570 --> 00:38:51,260
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

829
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:04,200
Your deskmate didn't
come to school for days.

830
00:39:04,290 --> 00:39:05,260
He's more handsome than before.

831
00:39:07,140 --> 00:39:09,510
Duan Xiao is in your class?

832
00:39:09,830 --> 00:39:10,710
Yep.

833
00:39:11,430 --> 00:39:12,470
But he didn't show his presence.

834
00:39:12,960 --> 00:39:14,050
He's on sick leave.

835
00:39:14,130 --> 00:39:16,070
He's laid up at home with a fever.

836
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:19,160
Let's go.

837
00:39:19,250 --> 00:39:20,580
Come to my home and eat together.

838
00:39:20,670 --> 00:39:21,090
Go.

839
00:39:21,170 --> 00:39:22,200
Hurry up, Hua.

840
00:39:27,490 --> 00:39:28,200
Ba Dan.

841
00:39:28,290 --> 00:39:29,270
Cheer up.

842
00:39:35,610 --> 00:39:37,170
[Peony Hotel]

843
00:39:40,750 --> 00:39:41,690
Good shot!

844
00:39:49,500 --> 00:39:50,200
Hello,

845
00:39:50,290 --> 00:39:51,310
it's Peony Hotel.

846
00:39:51,490 --> 00:39:53,510
Hello, I'm Li Jin Bu.

847
00:39:57,210 --> 00:39:58,190
What's wrong?

848
00:39:59,500 --> 00:40:00,080
You are sick,

849
00:40:00,170 --> 00:40:01,800
aren't you?

850
00:40:02,970 --> 00:40:04,320
It doesn't matter.

851
00:40:04,610 --> 00:40:06,030
A little cold.

852
00:40:06,330 --> 00:40:07,400
Okay.

853
00:40:07,620 --> 00:40:08,770
Uh,

854
00:40:08,860 --> 00:40:09,870
just greeting.

855
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:11,580
Take it easy.

856
00:40:11,770 --> 00:40:12,850
I'm a man.

857
00:40:12,940 --> 00:40:13,920
I'll recover soon.

858
00:40:14,260 --> 00:40:15,750
And one more thing.

859
00:40:16,170 --> 00:40:17,970
I've just transferred to your class today.

860
00:40:18,050 --> 00:40:19,590
We're classmates now.

861
00:40:20,810 --> 00:40:21,750
What?

862
00:40:22,180 --> 00:40:23,060
That's right.

863
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:26,950
I'll come back tomorrow.

864
00:40:27,610 --> 00:40:28,830
Well, see you tomorrow.

865
00:40:28,930 --> 00:40:29,810
See you tomorrow.

866
00:40:49,090 --> 00:40:50,070
Morning.

867
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,660
Why are you here?

868
00:40:52,770 --> 00:40:53,560
Go to school.

869
00:40:53,650 --> 00:40:54,440
Since we're on the way,

870
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:55,600
let's go together.

871
00:40:57,290 --> 00:40:58,840
But we don't live near each other

872
00:40:58,930 --> 00:41:01,000
and we never go to school together.

873
00:41:01,540 --> 00:41:03,010
All in all, we have the same destination.

874
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:04,210
I'll give Li Jin Bu a ride

875
00:41:04,300 --> 00:41:05,550
and you take care of yourself.

876
00:41:05,640 --> 00:41:06,520
Follow me.

877
00:41:16,130 --> 00:41:18,240
You've wasted too long
on looking for the girls.

878
00:41:18,330 --> 00:41:20,080
I haven't really seen their faces.

879
00:41:20,170 --> 00:41:21,350
Not very impressive.

880
00:41:21,430 --> 00:41:22,630
It's too hard.

881
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:24,660
I remember there's a stout girl.

882
00:41:24,790 --> 00:41:25,250
You're right.

883
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,640
A fatty.

884
00:41:28,770 --> 00:41:30,760
Just look like her.

885
00:41:30,850 --> 00:41:32,350
With curly hairs

886
00:41:32,430 --> 00:41:34,070
and broad face.

887
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:38,240
It's her!

888
00:41:38,330 --> 00:41:38,820
Halt!

889
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:40,160
You got the wrong person!

890
