919
00:42:25,250 --> 00:42:27,230
Hurry up.

920
00:42:29,140 --> 00:42:31,190
The game today was terrible.

921
00:42:33,610 --> 00:42:34,330
Du...

922
00:42:34,420 --> 00:42:35,330
Ba Dan!

923
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:35,770
What?

924
00:42:35,860 --> 00:42:36,090
Hey!

925
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:36,440
Don't move.

926
00:42:36,530 --> 00:42:36,970
What happened?

927
00:42:37,060 --> 00:42:37,830
Move back.

928
00:42:37,910 --> 00:42:38,790
Um,

929
00:42:39,610 --> 00:42:40,630
what's wrong?

930
00:42:41,050 --> 00:42:42,150
Nothing.

931
00:42:44,420 --> 00:42:45,570
Chen Jun He.

932
00:42:45,660 --> 00:42:47,330
We're in the school.

933
00:42:47,420 --> 00:42:48,410
Who are you?

934
00:42:48,500 --> 00:42:49,920
It's none of your business.
